  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK378">
<l>tuṟappārmaṟ ṟuppura villā ruṟaṟpāla</l>
<l>vūṭṭā kaḻiyu meṉiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The destitute will renounce desire (and become ascetics), if (fate) do not make them suffer the hindrances to which they are liable, and they pass away.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
